Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  這種壓力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有敵人攻擊
