Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  妮娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這散佈領域是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然出現了新的Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  大部隊似乎因敵人的增援  捕獲Gundam失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗  這種事…
