Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Over Flags  格拉哈姆·艾卡上級大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam捕獲失敗  請求增援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊屏蔽範圍擴大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的話  為什麼之前一直不使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要做什麼  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部  能聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是帕特里克  快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死  接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼才能回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅發來的密碼電文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam四機均健在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在返回太平洋第六地點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
